sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Notebook<br/>(Jupyter/Workbench)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>(Python Client)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP, 6379/TCP, 10001/TCP
    participant RayWorkers as Ray Worker Pods
    participant Route as OpenShift Router

    Note over User, RayWorkers: Flow 1: Cluster Creation

    User->>SDK: Cluster(ClusterConfiguration(...))
    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/localqueues<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: LocalQueue list (default queue)
    SDK->>SDK: Generate RayCluster YAML<br/>from base-template.yaml
    SDK->>SDK: Wrap in AppWrapper CR<br/>(if appwrapper=True)
    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST AppWrapper/RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: CR Created
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: AppWrapper queued
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Admit workload
    K8sAPI->>KubeRay: RayCluster CR reconcile
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create head/worker pods
    K8sAPI->>RayHead: Pod scheduled
    K8sAPI->>RayWorkers: Pods scheduled
    RayHead->>RayWorkers: GCS connection<br/>6379/TCP

    Note over User, RayWorkers: Flow 2: Job Submission

    User->>SDK: cluster.job_client.submit_job(...)
    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET routes (OpenShift)<br/>or GET ingresses (K8s)
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: Ray Dashboard URL
    SDK->>Route: Resolve Ray Dashboard Route
    Route-->>SDK: Dashboard endpoint
    SDK->>RayHead: POST /api/jobs/<br/>8265/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OpenShift)
    RayHead-->>SDK: Job ID
    RayHead->>RayWorkers: Distribute work<br/>Ray protocol
    RayWorkers-->>RayHead: Results
    User->>SDK: client.get_job_status(job_id)
    SDK->>RayHead: GET /api/jobs/{id}<br/>8265/TCP
    RayHead-->>SDK: Job status + logs

    Note over User, RayWorkers: Flow 3: TLS Certificate Generation

    User->>SDK: generate_cert.generate_tls_cert(name, ns)
    SDK->>K8sAPI: GET secrets (ca-secret-*)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: CA cert + key
    SDK->>SDK: Generate client cert<br/>RSA-2048, SHA-256<br/>signed by cluster CA
    SDK-->>User: TLS cert files<br/>tls-{name}-{ns}/
    User->>RayHead: RAY_USE_TLS=1<br/>10001/TCP mTLS
